{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I, I've now found out it's an illness called edema, if that's pronounced correctly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never really understand that illness and why I should have got it, but-- And, and the strange thing is that I've seen many films, and I've read many books, and I've never, ever seen anybody else-- everybody's always skeletons.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've never seen anybody who has got bloated and swollen legs like I had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I've never seen any books where people seem to have mentioned this edema.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But yeah, anyway, that's what I had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And people say, you get that just before you die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So maybe that's why you don't see many people like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and that is my excuse why I didn't do so good in, on the food and everything else in our first days of liberation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just wasn't really with it, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was in bad condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on top of that, I actually got typhus then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and so did my brother, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were both taken away by the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were taken to a Russian army hospital near Riesa-- quite a distance from Trebitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there, [NON-ENGLISH] and me, we both had typhus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had very high temperatures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had good treatment there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we spent two weeks in the hospital there, and we survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went back to Trebitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And by that time, all the people off the train were living in Trebitz, in the houses and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was very difficult for us to fit in, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we, we said, basically, we really wanted to go back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There's no point in hanging on there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
